    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee dsihwoja Gileadá eekſch Bahsana/ un eekſch wiꞥ- na peederrigahm Weetahm / un eekſch wiﬀeem Sarona Preekſch- Pilstahteem lihds winnu Gal- leem.\n"
