    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo dauds kritte eewainte- ti/ tapehz ka winnu Raufchana no Deewa bija. Un tee dsihwo- ja winnu Weetâ/ lihds tam Laikam/ kad tee aiswesti ktua.\n"
